  <entry>
    <title>【PC】琥珀结晶</title>
    <link href="https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/fec14c38.html"/>
    <id>https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/fec14c38.html</id>
    <published>2024-05-16T03:54:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-16T03:54:52.875Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>在过去有关系很好的6个青梅竹马。</p><p>他们相互为友情发誓，结下坚固的牵绊……本来曾是那样的。<br>但不知不觉间中断了交流，最终是变得疏远了。</p><p>那之后过了7年的岁月，在不再回想过去的时候……</p><p>主人公和仰慕自己的后辈、同学朋友们过着平稳的学园生活。<br>在那样的主人公面前，过去青梅竹马们的身影再次出现时——</p><p>差不多快忘掉的那些记忆回现，故事的序幕，又再拉开。</p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%60%E3%80%90%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E3%80%91/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96galgame%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%20part21/Soldier%20Blue/%5B090123%5D%5B%E3%82%B3%E3%83%83%E3%83%88%E3%83%B3%E3%82%BD%E3%83%95%E3%83%88%5D%20%E3%82%A2%E3%83%B3%E3%83%90%E3%83%BC%E3%82%AF%E3%82%A9%E3%83%BC%E3%83%84.rar"   title="点击下载"><i class="red larger"></i><span>点击下载</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
